    "description": "<p>INC pest is an elite Singapore-based pest management company. We began servicing Singapore’s pest control needs in 2014, then proceeded to expand our services in Shanghai.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As an INC Pest client, you can leave the work to us and be guaranteed efficient and effective pest control results, at an affordable cost. INC Pest is here to take care of you. We are proud to be one of the leading&nbsp;<u><strong>pest control companies</strong></u>&nbsp;in Singapore providing quality&nbsp;<u><strong>pest control service</strong></u>&nbsp;to residents and businesses all around the island.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Your Perferred Pest Management Partner</p>",
